		<blockquote class="quoteContainer"><div class="quote">The other annoyance is that every time I restart the transmission daemon it alters the permissions on my watch and download folders.  I keep having to ssh into my jail and do &quot;chmod -R a+w&quot; so that I can access them as a samba share.</div><div class="quoteExpand">Click to expand...</div></blockquote>
	</aside>
</div>jm0, I don&#039;t use transmission, but this seems suspiciously like a bug. It&#039;ll probably get fixed at some point, but you can help make sure it does if you open a ticket at support.freenas.org
				</blockquote>
			</article>
			
			
		</div>
		
		
		
		
		
		
				
